y":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"The truth is obedience and respect should not be automatic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , they should be earned<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a7f6c97e9f057c53809fa2fbecff2aac32c984","tid":323932,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"連呢個位都唔幫，等幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f12772566e8cdca360c0338cb70eed22a74f41","tid":323932,"uid":103294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:19:38.000Z","msg":"我老母成日係長輩前侮辱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫佢？不了"},{"pid":"b6e6c9a7e9bfaa29c737f5ec9f504977ac9dd0d5","tid":323932,"uid":126690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7de645f6159091f943b3b973ad0484c67fabb316","tid":323932,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"有道理唔怕駁 有道理嘅都唔比你駁就係廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9ae5598fa5467a264f71b1ac2071c4a4a90fbb","tid":323932,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:37:06.000Z","msg":"即使你會比人屌返轉頭都要出聲"},{"pid":"71a78d5684e5b862f005a7f4612d09d1471f1ab3","tid":323932,"uid":23451,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"由細到大都會<br />\n有個親戚成日借d意俾說話我呀爸呀媽聽<br />\n直接串尻過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呀媽之後雖然口講叫我尊重長輩<br />\n但我好肯定我屌尻佢果陣我呀媽有暗爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我由細到大係d親戚眼中都係曳d搞事果個<br />\n相反就覺得我呀哥好乖<br />\n我有果句講果句<br />\nd親戚講我老豆老母我會十倍奉還返俾d八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾佢地都唔撚夠膽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955df0e86ffb5a82ba012a3cc71a8039cad8ab10","tid":323932,"uid":23451,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大都會<br />\n有個親戚成日借d意俾說話我呀爸呀媽聽<br />\n直接串尻過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呀媽之後雖然口講叫我尊重長輩<br />\n但我好肯定我屌尻佢果陣我呀媽有暗爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我由細到大係d親戚眼中都係曳d搞事果個<br />\n相反就覺得我呀哥好乖<br />\n我有果句講果句<br />\nd親戚講我老豆老母我會十倍奉還返俾d八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾佢地都唔撚夠膽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有次直頭反枱咁撚滯，係酒樓食飯，有個親戚講我對我屋企人唔尊重，原因係我屋企由細到大都嗌老豆老母全名(幾歲開始就係咁)，嗌左廿幾年，我地成家都係咁廿幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我大聲講話[我呀爸呀媽都未出聲幾時到你出聲，唔通好似你個仔咁廿幾三十歲仲要成日係條街咀你好似細路咁嗌你，係人見到都覺佢裙腳仔咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ]<br />\n之後餐飯成枱靜撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我老豆老母果次一句都冇屌過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後條八婆個仔聽到又紅到臉哂，後期佢個仔都開始會反駁下佢老母話佢已經好大個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想仲好似細路咁，完美既結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad24ed5fcddf1347189c16071b43f35f8eca836","tid":323932,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲威脅我佢地死左我地成世唔安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佢講：睇下到時有冇人燒野比你咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4885771c09684e542efdf488462cbf29322483a","tid":323932,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大都會<br />\n有個親戚成日借d意俾說話我呀爸呀媽聽<br />\n直接串尻過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/